        "synopsis": {
            "value": "A fairy is hit by an arrow he shot himself. He falls in love with a woman.\n\nCheon Sang-Hyuk (Jang Dong-Yoon) is a charismatic fairy, who easily makes woman fall in love with him. 500 years ago, his wings were burned. To restore his wings, he went through 27 metamorphoses. On his 28th time, he gets involved with Oh Baek-Ryeon (Nana).\n\nOh Baek-Ryeon is a veterinarian and she works at an animal clinic. She is a pretty woman. She has had many men fall in love with her because of her attractiveness. Whenever these men got into a romantic relationship with her, they always had a near-death experience and would then runaway from her. Because of the bad luck, Oh Baek-Ryeon is not dating anyone, but she badly wants to meet a man of fate.",
